\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma*
The length of the Jordan chain of 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{n}$
\end_inset

 is given by the number of prime factors 
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega\left(n\right)$
\end_inset

, so that 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
